帮帮我们家。” 10月14日，华商报大风新闻记者联系到长安区交警队，工作人员表示，事故目前正在处理中，不便透露具体信息。西安一小米SU7疑超速行驶撞上公交站台，致1死1伤！家属：妈妈急需输血抢救"},"attached_info":"Cj8IusSSv7fFsvRgEAMaCTExMTE0ODM1MyDO8LO4BjAAOERAB3IJODkzOTU1MzUxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"93 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"8_1728963195.797730","card_id":"Q_885015298","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":885015298,"title":"深圳今年再现「日光盘」，332 套房 3 个半小时售罄，反映了什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/885015298","type":"question","created":1728893923,"answer_count":31,"follower_count":50,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[395,1740,3451,3865,105508],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"据证券时报14日报道，10月13日，位于深圳龙华区的深业上城学府开盘，超744批客户“抢”332套房。记者从乐有家研究中心获悉，该项目经过3个多小时的选房后告罄。 据了解，该项目销售均价7.6万元/平方米，于当日下午3点开盘，经3个半小时售罄，本批房源销售总金额约26亿元。 据深圳市房地产业协会10月13日晚间披露的信息，今年深圳登记比超1：1的项目仅有7个，但开盘当天“日光”的，此前仅有海德园项目；龙华深业上城学府是今年深圳的第二个“日光盘”。深圳现“日光盘”！332套房3个半小时售罄 | 每经网"},"attached_info":"Cj8IusSSv7fFsvRgEAMaCTExMTE0NDgyNCDjp7O4BjAAODJACHIJODg1MDE1Mjk4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"88 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-68172a6c91f57b3f51d13674f362d9af_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"9_1728963195.798614","card_id":"Q_826792556","card_label":{"type":"hot","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":826792556,"title":"如果未来科技让望远镜继续发展，我们还能看到什么？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/826792556","type":"question"